text:
ESRS E1 paragraph 38 states that the undertaking with operations in high-climate impact sectors
shall further disaggregate their total energy consumption from fossil sources by:
(a) fuel consumption from coal and coal products;
(b) fuel consumption from crude oil and petroleum products;
(c) fuel consumption from natural gas;
(d) fuel consumption from other fossil sources; and
(e) consumption of purchased or acquired electricity, heat, steam or cooling from fossil
sources.
